  "title": "Assistant Operations Manarger (Housekeeping)",
  "description": "<h2>Job Description</h2><ul><li><p>Supervise cleaning teams to ensure compliance with SOPs and service standards.</p></li><li><p>Monitor daily operations and conduct site inspections with clients (e.g. CAG); follow up on cleaning gaps.</p></li><li><p>Plan work schedules and deploy manpower efficiently.</p></li><li><p>Review cleaning job reports and prepare information for monthly meetings.</p></li><li><p>Compile basic operational data and propose improvements to work processes.</p></li><li><p>Conduct daily roll calls and team briefings.</p></li><li><p>Manage staff performance and provide feedback for improvement.</p></li><li><p>Handle feedback, investigations, and incident report submissions.</p></li><li><p>Ensure operational KPIs are met.</p></li><li><p>Perform other reasonable ad-hoc operational duties as assigned.</p></li></ul><h2>Job Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>3 years of relevant working experience</strong> in cleaning operations or a related field.</p></li><li><p>Able to work at <strong>East location(s)</strong>.</p></li><li><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, with <strong>alternate weekend duties</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Good communication and basic supervisory skills.</p></li></ul><h2>Remuneration</h2><ul><li><p><strong>Salary:</strong> SGD <strong>3,400 – 3,800</strong>, commensurate with experience.</p></li></ul>",
